*After this season Universidad de Guadalajara bought the Torreon franchise;
*the two 2nd division semifinalists, Universidad de San Luis (who changed
*their name to Atlético Potosino (San Luis)) and Unión de Curtidores (León), 
*were also invited to the first Division to increase the number of teams to 20.



